</paragraph>
<paragraph id="79F4FEAD79B50C1166CA7CAA20D37A21" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
Brazil. 
<normalizedToken id="381277A274126B814C6143192A526144" originalValue="São">Sao</normalizedToken>
Paulo. Apiahy, Feb 1891(fl), 
<emphasis id="4636AF2C9D837D80A10D0FC14BD600E4" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">J.I. Puiggari 3711</emphasis>
